    <h1>Maestros</h1>

    <h2>Maestros Rules</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Participants are allowed to register multiple squads, provided that each squad is officially registered with the league.</li>
      <li>A registration fee of KES 300 is required per participant.</li>
      <li>At the end of each gameweek, the weekly champion shall receive KES 50 from each participant. This payment must be completed before the start of the next gameweek.</li>
      <li>In the event of a tie in gameweek points, the participant with the highest overall points will be declared the winner.</li>
      <li>There is no limit to the number of transfers allowed during the league.</li>
      <li>New participants joining after the league has commenced must pay a registration fee of KES 400.</li>
      <li>Registration fees are non-refundable under any circumstances.</li>
      <li>Failure to remit payment to three consecutive weekly champions will result in disqualification from the league.</li>
      <li>Only registered teams will be allowed to participate.</li>
    </ul>

